er which you may be eligible for a refund and the process for requesting one.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200\">Subscription Refunds</h2><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2\">Refunds for our subscription services are subject to the following conditions:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300\"><li class=\"mb-1\">You may request a full refund within 14 days of your initial purchase if you&#x27;re not satisfied with our service.</li><li class=\"mb-1\">No refunds will be provided after the 14-day period has expired.</li><li class=\"mb-1\">For annual subscriptions, a pro-rated refund may be considered at our discretion if requested within 30 days.</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200\">One-time Purchases</h2><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2\">For one-time purchases or credits:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300\"><li class=\"mb-1\">Refunds may be issued within 7 days of purchase if the service was not used.</li><li class=\"mb-1\">Partial refunds may be offered if only a portion of purchased credits have been used.</li><li class=\"mb-1\">No refunds will be issued for completed services or fully consumed credits.</li></ul></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200\">Service Disruptions</h2><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300\">If our service experiences significant disruptions affecting your ability to use the platform, we may offer compensation in the form of service credits or, in certain circumstances, a partial refund. Significant disruptions are determined at our discretion.</p></section><section><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-200\">How to Request a Refund</h2><p class=\"text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 mb-2\">To request a refund, please follow these steps:</p><ol class=\"list-decimal pl-5